Author: nhatnhatkhongnhi
Title: [ICO][ANN] EiraCube Ecosystem bridges digital and traditional retail
Body: ONE-STOP SOLUTION TO PUT THE PRODUCT ON THE EIRACUBE SHELVES IN THE LEADING SHOPPING CENTRES ACROSS THE WORLD  Simplicity is at the heart of the EiraCube concept. For merchants, it’s a straight forward process of renting a shelf and sending us the products. We will then take care of all the marketing, sales and transactions. For consumers, the EiraCube is a giant, cool looking, interactive vending machine. You simply browse the products and purchase using a credit or debit card and your product is dispensed to you immediately. Check out our video to find out more.

Author: eiracube
Title: [ICO][ANN] EiraCube Ecosystem bridges digital and traditional retail
Body: Here is the full story: Konstantin had a dream of creacting his "know-how", which was developed only by him and he found eirotech robotics company in Dublin. Afterwards, Eirotech robotics represented this idea as their own creation. They changed the terms of our agreement and we didn't accept it.We decided to break a contract with eirotech robotics and to find a new R&D centre. During the last few months we made a huge step.We have found new partners, who are using more advanced high-tech innovations and started to cooperate with them.

Author: eiracube
Title: [ICO][ANN] EiraCube Ecosystem bridges digital and traditional retail
Body: We aren't EiraTech project, EiraTech is just one of our robots supplier, who started to change the terms of our agreement as soon as they found out that we are going for ICO.  All EiraTech announcements about the ownership are fake. If they are so confident in what the say, let them confirm the documents. The employees who expressed their disagreement were on temporary contracts that we haven't extended and it's not our fault. They are removed from the website.
